Version 3.0 for Linux was released on March 8, 2001.
I haven't tried it yet.
In the free version, security features (java, javascript, etc.) are disabled.

mkdir ~/tmp/webwasher-install
cd ~/tmp/webwasher-install
wget http://www.webwasher.com/download/webwasher-3.0-linux-i386.tar.gz
tar zxf webwasher-3.0-linux-i386.tar.gz
sudo webwasher.install
